<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ortlieb Wolf, Pfleger zu Murach</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen des Diebstahls an Friedrich [von Cham], Bürger zu Nürnberg, seine schon lange andauernde Abwesenheit mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_18" id="8r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_18_r2l1"><expan>Ortlıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l3">pfleger cʒu Murach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_18_r2l4"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her pfleger Als Jr vns <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von fridrich Cramers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l5"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Burgers vnd eins <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen ~ der Jm ſein kremereÿ ver </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l6">ſtoln hab etc . dauon <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir vormals niht gevviſʒt noch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l7"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir dancken <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit fleiſſıklıch ſölichs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbens</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l8">gutenvvillens . Vnd thun euch cʒevviſſen . daʒ vvir nach dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l9">Fricʒen Cramer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> geſant heten vnd Jm das alſo cʒevviſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l10">getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolten . So iſt Er cʒu dercʒeit niht anheim . vnd iſt auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l11">etvvielange niht anheim geweſen . Vnd iſt vns geſagt worden daʒ Er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l12">in <expan>etvvielang<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit niht herheim kumen werde . da mügt Jr ew wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l13">nach richten . <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvo vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit auch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l14">beweiſen möchten . das teten vvir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> xpi </ab>
<note place="bottomleft">
<ab facs="#facs_18_r1l2"><expan>no<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>l<ex>itte</ex>r<ex>am</ex></expan> <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> <expan>ſc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>am</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r1l3"><expan>p<ex>er</ex>tin<ex>emus</ex></expan> infra</ab>
</note>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_18" id="8r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ortlieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Wolff, pfleger czu Murach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her pfleger, als ir uns <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                        von Fridrich Cramers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers, und eins
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, der im sein kremerey verstoln
                        hab etc., davon <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir vormals niht gewiszt noch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                            <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dancken <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        erberkeit fleissiklich sölichs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibens</expan> und
                        guten willens und thun euch cze wissen, daz wir nach dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> Friczen Cramer
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> gesant heten und im das also czewissen getan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolten. So ist er czu derczeit niht
                        anheim und ist auch etwielange niht anheim gewesen; und ist uns gesagt
                        worden, daz er in <expan>etwielang<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit niht herheim
                        kumen werde. Da mügt ir ew wol nach richten. <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit auch lieb
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft beweisen möchten das teten wir
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> Christi. <app>
<note place="bottomleft">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>l<ex>itte</ex>r<ex>am</ex></expan>
<expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
<expan>sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>am</ex></expan>
<expan>p<ex>er</ex>tin<ex>emus</ex></expan> infra </note>
</app></ab></div>
